text: Karatovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Karatovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 267 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 42 km from Tuymazy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Karatovo
